st.  Porter (Gibson) is violent, at times even cruel and the other characters aren't much better; some are worse.  Every character is from the wrong side of the tracks, even the cops are on the take and there are no punches pulled.  The only character you can really feel is a \"good guy\" is Rose, the stereotypical Callgirl with a heart of gold (although it's maybe only 10 karat, not a real 24 karat heart).\n\nNevertheless, you will root for Porter.  Frankly, I don't think anyone else could have pulled off this role and still kept the support of the audience like Gibson did, but then he generally always plays the good guy with a twist.  This time, the twist is a little more savage than usual.\n\nAll in all, if you enjoy the occasional violent romp on the big screen and you're a fan of Mel Gibson; Payback is worth seeing.", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "worstRating": "1", "bestRating": "10", "ratingValue": "8"}}, "duration": "PT1H40M", "cast_and_character": [{"actor": {"@type": "Person", "url": "/name/nm0000154/?ref_=tt_cl_t1", "name": "Mel Gibson"}, "character_and_episodes": [{"url": "/title/tt0120784/characters/nm0000154?ref_=tt_cl_t1", "name": "Porter"}]}, {"actor": {"@type": "Person", "url": "/name/nm0004742/?ref_=tt_cl_t3", "name": "Maria Bello"}, "character_and_episodes": [{"url": "/title/tt0120784/characters/nm0004742?ref_=tt_cl_t3", "name": "Rosie"}]}, {"actor": {"@type": "Person", "url": "/name/nm0004886/?ref_=tt_cl_t5", "name": "Bill Duke"}, "character_and_episodes": [{"url": "/title/tt0120784/characters/nm0004886?ref_=tt_cl_t5", "name": "Det. Hicks"}]}, {"actor": {"@type": "Person", "url": "/name/nm0001278/?ref_=tt_cl_t7", "name": "John Glover"}, "character_and_episodes": [{"url": "/title/tt0120784/characters/nm0001278?ref_=tt_cl_t7", "name": "Phil"}]}, {"actor": {"@type": "Person", "url": "/name/nm0005154/?ref_=tt_cl_t9", "name": "Lucy Liu"}, "character_and_episodes": [{"url": "/title/tt0120784/characters/nm0005154?ref_=tt_cl_t9", "name": "Pearl"}]